    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This specimen remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible signs of wear and reflecting a level of care rarely seen on the secondary market. From its flawless exterior finish to its pristine, factory-fresh interior, this automobile represents an uncompromising acquisition for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Professional inspections are encouraged to confirm its peerless state.",
