      "description": "Hi there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept and hand-washed. You really have to see it to believe how pristine it is. I'm looking for a new home for it where it'll be just as loved!",
